text: Ekaterina Voronina () is a 1957 Soviet drama movie directed by Isidor Annensky.ЕКАТЕРИНА ВОРОНИНА It stars Lyudmila Khityaeva, Sergey Bobrov, and Vera Pashennaya. ==Actors== *Lyudmila Khityaeva as Ekaterina Voronina *Sergey Bobrov as Voronin *Vera Pashennaya as Grandmother *Nadir Malishevsky as Lednyov *Ariadna Shengelaya as Irina *Vadim Medvedev as Mostovoy == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1957 drama movies Category:Soviet drama movies Category:Movies directed by Isidor Annensky
title: Ekaterina Voronina (movie)
